    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been totally pampered since day one, kept tucked away in the garage, and it is basically spotless inside and out. If you've been looking for that 'like-new' feeling but want to save a bit of money, this is definitely the one for you. Come take a look, you\u2019re going to love it!",
      "price": 46500.0,
