    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This FD3S RX-7 is a pristine example of Japanese engineering, featuring a numbers-matching 13B-REW rotary engine with exceptional compression across all rotor faces. The sequential twin-turbocharger system remains factory-spec, delivering linear boost through the precise 5-speed manual transmission and Torsen limited-slip differential. The chassis is remarkably rigid, retaining its signature 50/50 weight distribution and original double-wishbone suspension geometry. Every mechanical component, from the four-piston braking system to the vacuum lines, has been meticulously maintained to ensure peak performance. Finished in showroom-quality paint with a flawless interior, this vehicle is a definitive collector-grade specimen for the rotary purist.",
